            <title><![CDATA[Assassin's Creed Shadows Was Only Beaten By This One Game For A 2025 US Sales Record]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/assassins-creed-shadows-was-only-beaten-by-this-one-game-for-a-2025-us-sales-record/1100-6530500/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
